{"tid":2188421,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日本東京都增136宗確診　新西蘭再有患者死亡","createTime":"2020-09-04T08:30:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-04T08:30:04.000Z","uid":241764,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2f7e73211ed89699890cde6508728fdd59c1120b","tid":2188421,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T08:30:04.000Z","msg":"日本東京都新增136宗新型肺炎確診，累計超過2萬1千宗感染。<br />\n<br />\n另外，新西蘭3個多月以來再有新型肺炎患者死亡。新西蘭累計1700宗確診，23人死亡。總理阿德恩表示，新西蘭現時實行的防疫措施，將會實施至9月中。<br />\n<br />\n全文: <a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1547857-20200904.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1547857-20200904.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=HMiOmB7b1AqxO%2BCwCPl1ccjT01h1KCp2%2Bw2KB0oDRGE%3D&h=db880749\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1547857-20200904.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=9a231897\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1547857-20200904.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"}]}